&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a sharp, versatile Creative Strategist to take the reins on Mando. This isn&#39;t a support role. You&#39;ll own the creative end-to-end across most of our Mando ad formats: concepting, briefing, creator ops, and final sign-off. You&#39;ll be on a team working alongside some of the most talented senior creative minds in the industry, who will be in your corner as a sounding board and partner. The seat is set up so you grow fast, own real outcomes early, and learn from someone exceptional while doing it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own Mando creative across Stills, B-Roll, and Partnership/UGC ads. You lead concepting, briefing, and sign-off. Our senior strategist supports and pressure-tests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with our senior strategist on TV spots, supporting on agency selection and co-leading creative review.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run all creator operations for Mando partnership and UGC work: sourcing, briefing, contracting, payment, whitelisting, the whole pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop original ad ideas. Hooks, concepts, scripts. Bring them to the senior strategist for feedback and sharpen from there.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recut and remix existing ads quickly to generate high-volume creative iterations. Fast turnarounds are a superpower here.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with video editors to turn existing footage into fresh ad concepts. Brief clearly and review with a strong creative eye.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cut and produce ads yourself when needed. You won&#39;t always have a dedicated editor and that&#39;s okay.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pick up new tools fast. AI creative platforms, editing software, growth analytics. Get fluent quickly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay close to the customer. Watch ads, read comments, study reviews, and use those insights to inform every creative decision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
