&lt;p&gt;The Supply Planning team works with demand planning, distribution, and other cross-functional partners to develop production plans, optimize inventory, and ensure high customer fulfillment rates across both DTC and Retail channels. We balance service levels against inventory efficiency, and we take ownership of continuous improvement across our tools, processes, and outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
